BellSouth Advanced Systems, aunit of BellSouth Corp, said it has introduced a privatetelephone system, called BellSouth System 30, offering smallercompanies a wide range of advanced telecommunications services.    BellSouth said the services, aimed at companies requiringup to 20 telephones, include speed dialing for 500 frequentlycalled numbers, last number redial, conference calling andspeakerphones, among others.    The company said the System 30 has the capacity for 10outside lines. Reuter&#3;